data.description: Come check out this well maintained, solid brick home.   As you step through the front door you will be welcomed into an oversized living room and dining room.  Just off the dinning room is a charming kitchen that leads outside to the fenced in back yard.  Upstairs you will find three bedrooms and a full bathroom.  The house is close to stores, restaurants, the Reading Hospital and public transportation. Call today for your private showing!
